title: Looking for members for a Low Elo Bronze/Silver Ranked Team (Go Team Moose)
body: Join the Bronze club guys (aka Team M00se) for some ranked games, I consider myself to be a sound player with really good games but also some bad. I main Top/Support but can play anything really so if i can get some peeps to join in some fun ranked games and hopefully win then you can join the eseemed clan M00se :) (also the less salty the better, I know its a lot to ask)
